1. Ternary operator.

variable = condition? value true: value false.
example:
int balance, interest;
balance = 10;
interest = (balance == 1) ? 20 : 30;
interest = (balance == 10) ? 20 : 30;

2. SWITCH. Recommended for driver configuration.

 String driver = RunTest.setDriver("chromeDriver");
        switch (driver) {
            case "firefoxDriver":
                // some code
                System.out.println("firefoxDriver");
                break;
            case "chromeDriver":
                // some code
                System.out.println("chromeDriver");
                break;
            case "operaDriver":
                // some code
                System.out.println("operaDriver");
                break;
            default:
                //some code
                System.out.println("default browser");
        }

